NextCast.fm - A Podcast Player
================================

NextCast.fm is a fork of AntennaPod, an open-source podcast player
originally developed by the AntennaPod team and community contributors.

Original Project
----------------
AntennaPod
Repository: https://github.com/AntennaPod/AntennaPod
License: GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)

