Modifications Made
------------------
The following modifications have been made to the original AntennaPod project:

1. REBRANDING
   - Changed application ID from "de.danoeh.antennapod" to "fm.nextcast"
   - Changed application name from "AntennaPod" to "NextCast.fm"
   - Updated content provider authorities

2. VERSION RESET
   - Reset version to 1.0.0 for the fork

